@startuml

hide footbox
skinparam Shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor white
skinparam SequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Преподаватель" as Teacher
actor "Студент" as Student
participant "UI" as UI
participant "Бэкенд Веб-сервиса" as BE
participant "PNETLab" as PNET

Teacher -> UI: Выдает мероприятие с набором заданий
UI -> BE: POST /labs/<slug>/<lab_type>/
BE -> BE: CompetitionForm.save()\n+ handle_competition_users()

BE -> BE: m2m signal tasks_changed(post_add)
BE -> BE: generate_and_save_flags(instance, tasks)
BE -> BE: create_flag_deployment_task(...)
BE -> BE: queue.submit_task(task)\n(ThreadPoolExecutor)

BE -> PNET: login_user_to_pnet + create_pnet_lab_session_common
PNET --> BE: success, session ready

BE -> PNET: get_lab_topology
PNET --> BE: topology data (SSH-ноды)

loop Для каждой SSH-ноды из конфигурации
  BE -> PNET: turn_on_node(node_id)
  PNET --> BE: ack

  BE -> PNET: get_node_status(node_id)\n(до готовности)
  PNET --> BE: status
end

BE -> BE: create_ssh_tasks_for_lab_nodes()
BE -> BE: process_ssh_tasks()\n(доставка флагов по SSH)
BE -> BE: task.status = SUCCESS/FAILED

BE --> UI: Результат выдачи\n(_wait_for_flag_deployment)

Student -> UI: Отправляет ответ на задание
UI -> BE: POST /api/check_task_answers/
BE -> BE: Сверяет answer и generated_flags
BE --> UI: correct / incorrect

@enduml
